Package massbalance

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Equivalence
    Class for generating, reading, and writing the mass equivalence classes required for mass balanced randomization.
    EquivalenceClass
    Class representing the mass equivalence classes used for mass-balanced randomization.
    JMassBalance
    Graphical User Interface for mass-balanced randomization.
    MetabolicGraph
    Objects of this class represent a metabolic network as a directed weighted bipartite graph.
    Properties
    Class for parsing, graph creation and calculating properties of randomized networks.
    Randomize
    Main class for randomizing a MetabolicGraph using the pre-calculated mass equivalence classes.
    Utilities
    This class contains static methods for parsing compound masses, writing graph information, and merging property files.
    Vertex
    Basic vertex object representing compound and reaction vertices.
    VertexComparator
    Class for comparing and ordering vertices.
